title: Live, Laugh, Lu with Danny Pellegrino
itunes:title: Live, Laugh, Lu.
description: Jackie has a full Bravo binge sesh with Danny Pellegrino. They discuss all star housewives, Leo Dicaprio's sexcapades and why they will probably pass on renting Scheana Valetta's lake house. Si'bon, si'bon.
